      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward value for someone seeking dependable basic transportation or a practical project. It presents as an honest used car with everyday utility, making it a smart option for buyers who prioritize affordability and potential over cosmetics. A solid opportunity to get into a vehicle at an accessible price point.",
