    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runner that could make a great project, first car, or budget-friendly commuter for the right buyer. It\u2019s got character, a usable interior, and the kind of straightforward charm that makes it worth a look if you don\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC. If you want something cheap, approachable, and full of possibility, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or backup driver with strong underlying potential. It shows its age cosmetically and will need attention in a few areas, but it offers a straightforward platform for someone who appreciates a usable chassis and proven mechanical layout. Good candidate for a hands-on owner looking for affordable entry into ownership without spending big money up front. Priced to move and well-suited for a fixer-upper, parts donor, or practical around-town runabout.",
